 class=\"n\">zero_ne_one</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"err\">ğ•œ&#39;</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">normed_field</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">normed_ring</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ&#39;</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">normed_algebra</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ&#39;</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"err\">ğ•œ&#39;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">â‰ </span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"k\">begin</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">refine</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">norm_pos_iff</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mp</span> <span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">symm</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">rw</span> <span class=\"n\">normed_algebra</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">norm_one</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ&#39;</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">norm_num</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">end</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">lemma</span> <span class=\"n\">normed_algebra</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">to_nonzero</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"err\">ğ•œ&#39;</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">normed_field</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">normed_ring</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ&#39;</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">normed_algebra</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ&#39;</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">nonzero</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ&#39;</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"o\">{</span> <span class=\"n\">zero_ne_one</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">normed_algebra</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">zero_ne_one</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ</span> <span class=\"err\">ğ•œ&#39;</span> <span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
