    {
        "content": "<p>I think that Lean can't guess <code>ğ•œ</code> based on <code>ğ•œ'</code>, so <code>ğ•œ</code> should be an explicit argument. I don't know whether you want <code>ğ•œ'</code> to be explicit or not.</p>",
